.SH NAME
api-rest-generatorall \- the api-rest-generator comprehensive
reference (architecture, configuration, DDL dialects, type mapping,
template grammar, port discipline)
.SH OVERVIEW
This is the all-in-one
.B api-rest-generator
manual, modeled on
.BR zshall (1).
It concatenates every section so you can grep with `/`:
.RS 2
.PP
.B 1.  WHAT IT DOES
.RB "\(em " "schema in, fully-wired Spring Boot REST backend out"
.br
